text: Hai Nabi! Tharowangka ko manga Karomangka go so manga Wata a Ka a manga Babai, go so manga Babai ko Miyamaratiyaya, a sapungun iran ko mga olowiran go si-i ko manga Paras iran so manganditarun iran go so manga sapung iran ka an kadilongi so manga paras iran ago so manga Rarub iran ago so manga olo iran.
